I understand your lack of sleep

2
01:15:52.460 --> 01:15:53.930 
判断力不足  罗伯特
and coherency, Robert.

3
01:15:53.930 --> 01:15:55.390 
宝宝有无限空间
Babies can be anything,

4
01:15:55.400 --> 01:15:57.060 
